  * Capture-the-flag (CTF) competitions and training labs on
    infrastructure the operator owns or is authorized to test.
  * Security research, exploit development, and defensive hardening on
    systems the operator owns or has been granted permission to assess.
  * Educational use in controlled environments (e.g. the included
    target_builder generates intentionally vulnerable servers for
    training on isolated lab networks).

You MUST NOT use the ROP Tools Suite, any derivative work, or any
