  * Violate any applicable law, regulation, export control, or contract
    in the jurisdiction in which you operate or the jurisdiction of the
    target system.

Binaries produced by `target_builder` are intentionally vulnerable by
design. Do NOT deploy them on any network reachable by untrusted
parties. They are meant to run on isolated lab machines for exploit
development practice only.

